race.comment: AEROPLANE RUBY (7) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing seven from 14 starts. Finished in the minors latest when second (35.28) at The Gardens and may be close to breaking through. Sure to be about the mark. BLACK TIGER (8) was unfavoured last start but gave a huge sight when led for much of the way to place (35.00) at this track in a Grade 5 over 603m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Will give a great sight again. AVA'S BLUEY (2) doesn't win out of turn. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when third (30.10) at this track. Expected to feature. EUREKA ROBBIE (1) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.
